{"tid":1499259,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[以言入罪?]港鐵禁制令嘅重點喺呢度","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:03:23.000Z","uid":98411,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"075f913e60314a8f88657eaacce3f12cdd6b2f07","tid":1499259,"uid":98411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"港鐵於今晚9時45分成功向高院申請臨時禁制令，有關禁令有效至下周五。港鐵發言人表示，鑑於近日有人一而再、再而三地惡意破壞車站設施，以粗言穢語辱罵港鐵人員，威脅職員以至其他乘客的安全，港鐵今晚已獲得法庭的臨時禁制令，禁止任何人士非法地及有意圖地故意阻礙或干擾整個鐵路網絡（重鐵及輕鐵）車站及列車以及高速鐵路西九龍總站的正常使用、損壞任何財產或列車，以及<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">使用任何威脅、辱罵，淫褻或令人反感的語言，或故意干擾這些車站內任何港鐵人員</span></span>。臨時禁制令有效直至2019年8月30日。<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始,喺香港鬧人都會犯法?下一步係咪準備辱警罪立法?<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190823/59966448?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2oaQmbSqbv5QMlpHOCYGp6P_7rAmY06U-lxiDn2XH09Ic89X5NMLXbmlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59966448%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2oaQmbSqbv5QMlpHOCYGp6P_7rAmY06U-lxiDn2XH09Ic89X5NMLXbmlc&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6uEzQ5hKls32m7Ak2FFrcx0%3D&h=cdd6c8f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59966448%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2oaQmbSqbv5QMlpHOCYGp6P_7rAmY06U-lxiDn2XH09Ic89X5NMLXbmlc&h=4edc12ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190823/59966448?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2oaQmbSqbv5QMlpHOCYGp6P_7rAmY06U-lxiDn2